Leetcode - 121. Best Time to Buy and Sell Stock

Time Complexity - O(n)
Space Complexity - O(1)
Solution with inline description - 
```
class Solution:
    def maxProfit(self, prices: List[int]) -> int:
        min_price = prices[0]                           #tracking min_price at every day till date
        profit = 0                                      #result profit
        for i in range(1, len(prices)):                 #O(n) a single loop on prices list
            profit = max(profit, prices[i] - min_price) #maximising profit 
            if min_price > prices[i]:                   #considering lowest price at each loop and updating it 
                min_price = prices[i]
        
        return profit                                   #returning the maximised profit
```
